│ - March: 19 days                                                                                                     │
│ Total = 31 + 28 + 19 = 78 days                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                      │
│ So, total days from LMP to today = 166 (from 2013) + 78 (from 2014) = 244 days.                                      │
